documentation.text:
@notice Log Normal has three variable parameters:
 K - strike price
 sigma - volatility
 tau - time to expiry
 Swaps are validated by the trading function:
 Gaussian.ppf(x / L) + Gaussian.ppf(y / KL) = -sigma * sqrt(tau)
